@startuml ambient-sequence-l7
title Fluxo de requisição — Ambient, com Waypoint (L7)
' Caso real: payment-api -> payment-cache (ver istio/payment-cache.yaml)

participant "payment-api\n(app)" as A
participant "ztunnel\n(nó de payment-api)" as ZA
participant "waypoint\n(payment-hub)" as WP
participant "ztunnel\n(nó de payment-cache)" as ZB
participant "payment-cache\n(app)" as B

A -> ZA : GET /get-card-limit
activate ZA
ZA -> WP : mTLS HBONE\n(identidade de payment-api)
deactivate ZA
activate WP
WP -> WP : VirtualService (timeout 16s)\nAuthorizationPolicy\n(paths: /get-card-limit)
WP -> ZB : mTLS HBONE\n(identidade agora é do\nWAYPOINT, não mais de A)
deactivate WP
activate ZB
ZB -> ZB : o ztunnel de destino só\nenxerga "src=waypoint" —\npor isso a policy é anexada\nao waypoint (targetRefs),\nnão ao workload (selector)
ZB -> B : encaminha em claro
activate B
B --> ZB : resposta
deactivate B
ZB --> WP : mTLS HBONE
deactivate ZB
WP --> A : resposta (via ztunnels)
@enduml
